WEBVTT

00:00.800 --> 00:07.000
I think one of the things that really separates us from the high primates is that we're tool builders.

00:07.200 --> 00:14.550
And I read a study that measured the efficiency of locomotion for various species on the planet.

00:15.600 --> 00:18.000
The condor used the least energy to move a kilometer.

00:18.700 --> 00:25.050
And humans came in with a rather unimpressive showing about a third of the way down the list.

